---
title: Turkey Meatloaves with Herb Butter plus Creamy White Beans & Glazed Carrots
description: Get ready to elevate garlic-herb turkey meatloaves with a finishing drizzle of rosemary-infused hot honey butter. How good is that butter? So good you’ll toss it with tender roasted carrots, too! Serve it all with velvety mashed white beans swirled with rich, tangy crème fraîche for a restaurant-style meal right in your own kitchen.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66955929b0a47382be87029a-05218f76.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66955929b0a47382be87029a-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 820 kcal
  fat: 37 g
  saturated fat: 14 g
  carbohydrates: 72 g
  sugar: 25 g
  protein: 40 g
